snippet.title: Naiad - Extended Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
NAIAD / A game about nature. 
Immerse yourself in a relaxing and colorful exploration experience, flowing by a river.

Available on:
Steam (PC/Mac), PS5 / PS4, Xbox Series SX / Xbox One / Nintendo Switch
